<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A4106018" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Uklanjanje i ugradnja spremnika glavnog cilindra kočnice
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A4106015">Komponente glavnog cilindra kočnice</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Ne dozvolite da kočna tekućina dođe u dodir s obojenim površinama. Obojene površine će se oštetiti kočnom tekućinom. Ako je tekućina prolivena, odmah je isperite sa vodom.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A4106018001">
<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Očistite vanjsku površinu spremnika.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite glavni cilindar kočnice zajedno sa spremnikom sa servouređaja kočnice.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Specijalnim alatom uklonite zatik opruge (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A004">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-44310">
09916-44310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A410013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.801mm" ver = "01" gw = "138" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite spremnik (1) i uvodnice (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A410014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "70.866mm" ver = "01" gw = "152" gh = "184"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A4106018002">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Kada stavljate nove uvodnice, podmažite ih istom kočnom tekućinom kao i onom kojom punite spremnik prije namještanja novih uvodnica u glavni cilindar.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite spremnik na glavni cilindar kočnice.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Gurajte zatik opruge (2) specijalnim alatom, dok oba kraja na desnoj i lijevoj strani spremnika (1) ne postanu iste dužine.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A005">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-44310">
09916-44310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8C50A410025.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.650mm" ver = "01" gw = "193" gh = "110"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite glavni cilindar kočnice sa spremnikom na pojačalo kočnice.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
